{"title":"二分查找","uid":"d843ced03f40ac612213952de4b63ad2","slug":"二分查找","date":"2022-03-07T14:29:22.000Z","updated":"2022-03-07T15:46:12.925Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/二分查找.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"·二分查找\"><a href=\"#·二分查找\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"·二分查找\"></a>·二分查找</h1><ul>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"浅查一下吧\"><a href=\"#浅查一下吧\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"浅查一下吧\"></a>浅查一下吧</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-C++\" data-language=\"C++\"><code class=\"language-C++\">&#x2F;&#x2F;查找有序表中第一个出现的元素K（lower&#x3D;1）,最后一个出现的元素K(lower&#x3D;1)\nint BiSearch(int A[],int K,int lower)\n\t&#123;\n      int left&#x3D;0 , right&#x3D;A.size()-1 , mid;\n      while(left&lt;&#x3D;right)\n      &#123;\n        mid &#x3D; left + (right-left)&#x2F;2;\n        if(A[mid]&lt;K || (lower&amp;&amp;A[mid]&#x3D;&#x3D;K))\n        \tleft &#x3D; mid+1;\n        else\n        \tright &#x3D; mid-1;\n      &#125;\n      return left;\n\t&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"快速幂\"><a href=\"#快速幂\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"快速幂\"></a>快速幂</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-C++\" data-language=\"C++\"><code class=\"language-C++\">long long fastpow(long long a,long long b)&#x2F;&#x2F;求a^b\n&#123;\n\tlong long sum&#x3D;1,base&#x3D;a;\n     \twhile(b!&#x3D;0)\n     \t&#123;\n       \tif(b%2 &#x3D;&#x3D; 1)sum *&#x3D; base;\n       \tbase *&#x3D; base;\n       \tb &#x2F;&#x3D; 2;\n     \t&#125;\n     \treturn sum;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n","text":"·二分查找 浅查一下吧&#x2F;&#x2F;查找有序表中第一个出现的元素K（lower&#x3D;1）,最后一个出现的元素K(lower&#x3D;1) int BiSearch(int A[],int K,int lower) &#123; int left&#x3D;0 ,...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":727,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"algorithm","slug":"algorithm","count":4,"path":"api/tags/algorithm.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%C2%B7%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">·二分查找